item.title: Los Angeles to Copenhagen on Scandinavian Airlines (LAX to CPH)
item.description: Only cellphone photos in here, I apologize in advance! I booked a ticket on Scandinavian Airlines through Hopper. It wasn’t too bad - I ended up flying United (boo) on a quick layover in San Francisco, where I had to weave my way through to the international terminal. I knew I was at the right gate judging by the amount of blonde hair I saw waiting there patiently and quietly!
